  "remarks": "Siberian Service Company JSC is a leading company in the Russian energy sector. Siberian Service Company holds a large market share in oil well drilling services and contributes substantially to the development of the Russian energy sector. Therefore, Siberian Service Company JSC is involved in an economic sector providing a substantial source of revenue to the Government of the Russian Federation, which is responsible for the annexation of Crimea and the destabilisation of Ukraine.",
